Package gameClient.Game_DS

Class GameAlgo

java.lang.Object
gameClient.Game_DS.GameAlgo
public class GameAlgo
extends java.lang.Object
Represents the game's algorithms. game - is the game server. info - the game's information. algo - graph algorithm. pokemons - the game's Pokemons. agents - the game's Agents. handlingPokemons - an ArrayList representing the Pokemons who need to be caught. targets - includes the path for of any agent to his Pokemon. timer - includes the estimated time on which every Agent gets to his targeted Pokemon.
Author:
Shaked Aviad & Rotem Halbreich
